      <head>Bernhard Seidmann (1891-)</head>
      <div>
        <!-- BODY: -->
        <p><hi rend="bold">Bernhard Seidmann (1891-),</hi> Swiss conductor, founder-director in 1943 of the Zurich Motet Choir.</p>
        <p>Two items of correspondence are known to survive from Seidmann to Schenker, OC 44/49 and 50, July 8 and August 29, 1934, at which time he was living in Dresden.</p>
